Tried Chug Biergarten and it’s officially my new fave hangout spot!
From a variety of beers that hit all the right notes to food that totally surprised me—every bite was worth it. The butter chicken paratha? ICONIC. Dumplings, baos, crunchy cauliflower crisps, and a comforting plate of dal makhni with roti sealed the deal.
Great vibes, great food, and beer that keeps flowing—what more do you need?
